name: What's an NFT tho #001
description:
Like, y'all buying these?

We're proud to present the first ever NFT release from artist Suijiku. It's a play on words that acknowledges that this print is a satire of the NFT world, hence, the name of it... "What's an NFT tho?" More than a Non-Fungible token, What does it mean to you? 

Alt Text: Cyber punk inspired background with three skulls overlapped as the main subject.
